title: Introducing: Culpable Season 2
description:
Culpable is back for a new season with a new case.

On August 28, 2013, 22 year old Brittany Stykes was shot and killed while driving down Highway 68 in Brown County, Ohio. It’s been nearly a decade since her murder and the search for answers continues. Host Dennis Cooper and investigative journalist Jessica Noll work to unearth the truth around this story of a young mother whose life was cut short and the loved ones who have been left picking up the pieces. From Resonate Recordings and Tenderfoot TV, this is season 2 of Culpable. Available now on Apple Podcasts or wherever you get your podcasts. For ad free listening, subscribe to Tenderfoot+ at www.tenderfootplus.com.
